tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Student_Report (
  student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  student_name VARCHAR(50),
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  age INT,
  graduation_status BOOLEAN,
  program_outcome TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE student_demographics (
    student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name TEXT,
    last_name TEXT,
    age INT,
    gender TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE student_demographics (
    student_id INT,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE graduation_rates (
    graduate_id INT,
    student_id INT,
    graduation_year INT,
    graduation_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE program_outcomes (
    program_id INT,
    program_name VARCHAR(50),
    graduation_year INT,
    employment_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
    salary_median DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE enrollment (
    enrollment_id INT,
    student_id INT,
    program_id INT,
    enrollment_year INT,
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE student_demographics (
    student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR,
    last_name VARCHAR,
    gender VARCHAR,
    date_of_birth DATE
)

CREATE TABLE graduation_rates (
    graduation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    graduation_date DATE,
    program VARCHAR,
    graduation_status VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE program_outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program VARCHAR,
    outcome_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE student_programs (
    student_id INT,
    program VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE student_grades (
    student_id INT,
    course_id INT,
    grade VARCHAR
)
